==性质==
六苯基苯加[[氢|氢]]还原，可以得到六环己基苯和六环己基环己烷。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=142|issue=30|language=en|issn=0002-7863|date=2020-07-29|pages=12916–12920|doi=10.1021/jacs.0c04956|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/jacs.0c04956|title=From Hexaphenylbenzene to 1,2,3,4,5,6-Hexacyclohexylcyclohexane|accessdate=2020-08-24|author=Marcel Dillenburger, Zijie Qiu, Cheng-Wei Ju, Beate Müller, Svenja Morsbach, Dieter Schollmeyer, Akimitsu Narita, Klaus Müllen|archive-date=2020-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001183734/https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/jacs.0c04956|dead-url=no}}</ref>

